film.title: The Graduate
film.description: A disillusioned college graduate finds himself torn between his older lover and her daughter.

film.title: Rocky
film.description: Rocky Balboa, a small-time boxer from working-class Philadelphia, is arbitrarily chosen to take on the reigning world heavyweight champion, Apollo Creed.

film.title: The Dark Knight
film.description: When a vile young criminal calling himself the Joker suddenly throws the town into chaos, Batman begins to tread a fine line between heroism and vigilantism.

film.title: Toy Story
film.description: Woody, a good-hearted cowboy doll who belongs to a young boy named Andy, sees his position as Andy's favorite toy jeopardized when his parents buy him a Buzz Lightyear action figure.

film.title: Alien
film.description: In deep space, the crew of the commercial starship Nostromo is awakened from their cryo-sleep capsules halfway through their journey home to investigate a distress call from an alien vessel.

film.title: Braveheart
film.description: A film about bravery and patriotism.
